nc, Malvern, PA.[6] "Product Information. Amevive (alefacept)." Biogen, Cambridge, MA.[7] "Product Information. Taltz Autoinjector (ixekizumab)." Eli Lilly and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[8] "Product Information. Cosentyx (secukinumab)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.[9] "Product Information. Ilaris (canakinumab)." Novartis Pharmaceuticals, East Hanover, NJ.', 1767363024);
